entries.femaleVariant: They've gone whacked with these prices. A little more and CHOOH2'll cost more than diesel.
The greedy corpo bastards. Whatta they want? Tryin' to get us all on bikes?
Great plan. Sure their cash flow'll skyrocket.
Hang on, I know. It's all 'cause of the wheat harvest. Real bad year, apparently.
What's wheat got to do with it?
You serious? What do you think CHOOH2 comes from?
I couldn't give a shit. Why should I care what I put in my ride, so long as it runs?
